@cbornet sorry for getting back to this late. in general I like this grpc proxy. however since it is a new feature, would you mind writing up a PIP for this feature? when this feature is approved and merged, we can use that PIP for writing documentation for this feature.

You can find example PIPs here: - https://github.com/apache/pulsar/wiki

You can write is in your own gist. I will move your gist to the pulsar wiki when it is available.
